We have not been able to successfully rid ourselves of the sickness associated with the five dimensional geometry.  

In fact, we can do better than this.  We can T-dualize our solution to find a system which should have the same physics.  In the new geometry, the full sickness of this configuration becomes apparent.  Performing a T-duality along the  direction, we find a solution to IIA supergravity with the following metric.

